{"type":"user","uuid":"6a3ec5a1-bebb-4c19-9cf8-c49eb857a65a","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde4fead5acbdfb7f677edf39acfb","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-002: Task Breakdown\n   2→\n   3→## Setup Phase (T-001~T-009)\n   4→\n   5→- [x] [T-001] Create commands directory structure — file: src/bot/commands/index.js\n   6→\n   7→**目标**: 创建命令路由层的基础目录结构和入口文件。\n   8→**输入**: 无\n   9→**输出**: `src/bot/commands/` 目录及空文件结构\n  10→**验收**: 目录结构符合 plan.md，所有文件可正确导入\n  11→**复杂度**: Low\n  12→\n  13→---\n  14→\n  15→## Foundational Phase (T-010~T-099)\n  16→\n  17→- [x] [T-010] [US-7] [P] Implement command parser — file: src/bot/commands/parser.js\n  18→\n  19→**目标**: 实现命令解析器，将 Telegram 消息文本解析为结构化对象。\n  20→**输入**: Telegram 消息文本\n  21→**输出**: `ParsedCommand` 对象\n  22→**验收**:\n  23→- 正确解析命令名、子命令、参数、选项\n  24→- 支持别名映射\n  25→- 单元测试覆盖各种格式\n  26→**复杂度**: Medium\n  27→\n  28→- [x] [T-011] [P] Implement command registry — file: src/bot/commands/registry.js\n  29→\n  30→**目标**: 实现命令注册表，支持动态注册和查找命令。\n  31→**输入**: 命令元数据定义\n  32→**输出**: 注册表 API (register, get, getHelpText)\n  33→**验收**:\n  34→- 支持命令注册和查找\n  35→- 支持别名映射\n  36→- 生成帮助文本\n  37→**复杂度**: Medium\n  38→\n  39→- [x] [T-012] [P] Implement command validator — file: src/bot/commands/validator.js\n  40→\n  41→**目标**: 实现参数验证器，检查必填参数、类型和枚举值。\n  42→**输入**: `ParsedCommand`, `CommandMeta`\n  43→**输出**: `ValidationResult`\n  44→**验收**:\n  45→- 检查必填参数\n  46→- 验证类型和枚举值\n  47→- 生成明确的错误提示\n  48→**复杂度**: Medium\n  49→\n  50→- [x] [T-013] Implement error formatter — file: src/bot/commands/formatter.js\n  51→\n  52→**目标**: 实现错误消息格式化，生成用户友好的提示。\n  53→**输入**: 错误类型和上下文\n  54→**输出**: 格式化的错误消息\n  55→**验收**:\n  56→- 统一的错误消息格式\n  57→- 包含修正建议\n  58→**复杂度**: Low\n  59→\n  60→- [x] [T-014] Implement help text generator — file: src/bot/commands/help.js\n  61→\n  62→**目标**: 实现帮助文本生成器，动态生成命令使用说明。\n  63→**输入**: 命令名称（可选）\n  64→**输出**: 帮助文本\n  65→**验收**:\n  66→- 单命令帮助详细\n  67→- 全局命令列表简洁\n  68→**复杂度**: Low\n  69→\n  70→- [x] [T-015] Implement router entry point — file: src/bot/commands/index.js\n  71→\n  72→**目标**: 实现命令路由入口，整合 parser、registry、validator，统一处理命令。\n  73→**输入**: Telegram Context\n  74→**输出**: 命令处理结果（是否处理）\n  75→**验收**:\n  76→- 统一授权检查\n  77→- 解析 → 验证 → 分发流程\n  78→- 未知命令返回帮助\n  79→**复杂度**: Medium\n  80→\n  81→---\n  82→\n  83→## User Stories Phase (T-100+)\n  84→\n  85→- [x] [T-100] [US-1] Implement pipeline handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js\n  86→\n  87→**目标**: 实现 `/pipeline` 命令处理器，支持 run/status/logs/stop 子命令。\n  88→**输入**: `HandlerContext`\n  89→**输出**: 调用 pipeline-control-service 的结果\n  90→**验收**:\n  91→- 正确映射子命令到 service API\n  92→- 参数规范化\n  93→- 错误处理\n  94→**复杂度**: Medium\n  95→\n  96→- [x] [T-101] [US-2] [P] Implement bugfix handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/bugfix.js\n  97→\n  98→**目标**: 实现 `/bugfix` 快捷命令，代理到 pipeline handler。\n  99→**输入**: target 参数\n 100→**输出**: 启动 bugfix 管道\n 101→**验收**:\n 102→- 等同于 `/pipeline run --type=bugfix`\n 103→- 参数缺失时返回使用说明\n 104→**复杂度**: Low\n 105→\n 106→- [x] [T-102] [US-3] [P] Implement status handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js\n 107→\n 108→**目标**: 实现 `/status` 命令，显示所有运行中的管道。\n 109→**输入**: 无参数\n 110→**输出**: 管道状态列表\n 111→**验收**:\n 112→- 格式化状态输出\n 113→- 无管道时返回提示\n 114→**复杂度**: Low\n 115→\n 116→- [x] [T-103] [US-4] [P] Implement logs handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js\n 117→\n 118→**目标**: 实现 `/logs` 命令，获取管道日志。\n 119→**输入**: target 参数（可选）\n 120→**输出**: 日志文本或文件\n 121→**验收**:\n 122→- 日志 < 4000 字符分块发送\n 123→- 日志 >= 4000 字符发送为文件\n 124→**复杂度**: Medium\n 125→\n 126→- [x] [T-104] [US-5] [P] Implement stop handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js\n 127→\n 128→**目标**: 实现 `/stop` 命令，停止运行中的管道。\n 129→**输入**: target 参数（可选）\n 130→**输出**: 停止确认\n 131→**验收**:\n 132→- 调用 stopPipeline\n 133→- 显示确认消息\n 134→**复杂度**: Low\n 135→\n 136→- [x] [T-105] [US-6] Implement error formatter tests — file: tests/bot/commands/formatter.test.js\n 137→\n 138→**目标**: 为错误格式化器编写单元测试，验证 US-6 Error Guidance 需求。\n 139→**输入**: formatter.js\n 140→**输出**: 测试覆盖 > 90%\n 141→**验收**:\n 142→- 各种错误类型格式化测试\n 143→- 错误建议正确性测试\n 144→**复杂度**: Low\n 145→\n 146→- [x] [T-106] [US-1] Implement planner handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/planner.js\n 147→\n 148→**目标**: 实现 `/planner` 命令，支持 run/status/logs 子命令。\n 149→**输入**: `HandlerContext`\n 150→**输出**: 调用 pipeline-control-service (type=planner)\n 151→**验收**:\n 152→- 正确设置 pipelineType=planner\n 153→- 行为同 pipeline handler\n 154→**复杂度**: Low\n 155→\n 156→---\n 157→\n 158→## Polish Phase (T-900+)\n 159→\n 160→- [x] [T-901] [P] Write unit tests for parser — file: tests/bot/commands/parser.test.js\n 161→\n 162→**目标**: 为 parser.js 编写单元测试。\n 163→**输入**: parser.js\n 164→**输出**: 测试覆盖 > 90%\n 165→**验收**:\n 166→- 所有边界情况覆盖，测试通过\n 167→- 别名解析 `/p`, `/b`, `/s`, `/l` 测试通过\n 168→**复杂度**: Low\n 169→\n 170→- [x] [T-902] [P] Write unit tests for registry — file: tests/bot/commands/registry.test.js\n 171→\n 172→**目标**: 为 registry.js 编写单元测试。\n 173→**输入**: registry.js\n 174→**输出**: 测试覆盖 > 90%\n 175→**验收**: 注册、查找、别名测试通过\n 176→**复杂度**: Low\n 177→\n 178→- [x] [T-903] [P] Write unit tests for validator — file: tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js\n 179→\n 180→**目标**: 为 validator.js 编写单元测试。\n 181→**输入**: validator.js\n 182→**输出**: 测试覆盖 > 90%\n 183→**验收**: 各种验证场景覆盖\n 184→**复杂度**: Low\n 185→\n 186→- [x] [T-904] Write handler unit tests — file: tests/bot/commands/handlers/\n 187→\n 188→**目标**: 为所有 handler 编写单元测试。\n 189→**输入**: handlers/*.js\n 190→**输出**: 每个 handler 的测试文件\n 191→**验收**: Mock pipeline-control-service，验证调用参数\n 192→**复杂度**: Medium\n 193→\n 194→- [x] [T-905] Write integration tests — file: tests/integration/f002-command-router.integration.test.js\n 195→\n 196→**目标**: 编写集成测试，验证完整命令流程。\n 197→**输入**: 完整命令路由层\n 198→**输出**: E2E 测试覆盖\n 199→**验收**:\n 200→- 模拟 Telegram 消息\n 201→- 验证授权拦截\n 202→- 验证错误消息\n 203→**复杂度**: Medium\n 204→\n 205→- [x] [T-906] Integrate with telegram.js — file: src/bot/telegram.js\n 206→\n 207→**目标**: 将命令路由层集成到现有 Telegram Bot。\n 208→**输入**: 原有 telegram.js\n 209→**输出**: 更新后的 telegram.js\n 210→**验收**:\n 211→- 新命令注册到 bot\n 212→- 不影响现有功能\n 213→- 帮助文本更新\n 214→**复杂度**: Medium\n 215→\n 216→- [x] [T-907] Update help command — file: src/bot/telegram.js\n 217→\n 218→**目标**: 更新 `/help` 命令输出，包含新的管道命令。\n 219→**输入**: 新命令列表\n 220→**输出**: 更新后的帮助文本\n 221→**验收**: 帮助文本完整准确\n 222→**复杂度**: Low\n 223→\n 224→---\n 225→\n 226→## Task Summary\n 227→\n 228→| Phase | Count | Parallelizable |\n 229→|-------|-------|----------------|\n 230→| Setup | 1 | 0 |\n 231→| Foundational | 6 | 3 |\n 232→| User Stories | 7 | 4 |\n 233→| Polish | 7 | 3 |\n 234→| **Total** | **21** | **10** |\n 235→\n 236→## Dependency Graph\n 237→\n 238→```\n 239→T-001 (Setup)\n 240→    │\n 241→    ├──► T-010 [P] ──┐\n 242→    ├──► T-011 [P] ──┼──► T-015 ──► T-100 ──► T-106\n 243→    └──► T-012 [P] ──┘       │         │\n 244→            │                │         ├──► T-101 [P]\n 245→            └──► T-013 ──────┤         ├──► T-102 [P]\n 246→                            │         ├──► T-103 [P]\n 247→                            │         └──► T-104 [P]\n 248→                            │\n 249→                            └──► T-014\n 250→                                    │\n 251→                                    ▼\n 252→                    ┌───────────────────────────────────┐\n 253→                    │ T-901 [P]  T-902 [P]  T-903 [P]   │\n 254→                    │ T-105      T-904                   │\n 255→                    │           T-905                   │\n 256→                    │           T-906 ──► T-907         │\n 257→                    └───────────────────────────────────┘\n 258→```\n 259→\n 260→## Estimated Effort\n 261→\n 262→| Task | Complexity | Est. Time |\n 263→|------|------------|-----------|\n 264→| T-001 | Low | 0.5h |\n 265→| T-010 | Medium | 2h |\n 266→| T-011 | Medium | 2h |\n 267→| T-012 | Medium | 2h |\n 268→| T-013 | Low | 1h |\n 269→| T-014 | Low | 1h |\n 270→| T-015 | Medium | 2h |\n 271→| T-100 | Medium | 2h |\n 272→| T-101 | Low | 0.5h |\n 273→| T-102 | Low | 0.5h |\n 274→| T-103 | Medium | 1.5h |\n 275→| T-104 | Low | 0.5h |\n 276→| T-105 | Low | 1h |\n 277→| T-106 | Low | 0.5h |\n 278→| T-901 | Low | 1h |\n 279→| T-902 | Low | 1h |\n 280→| T-903 | Low | 1h |\n 281→| T-904 | Medium | 2h |\n 282→| T-905 | Medium | 2h |\n 283→| T-906 | Medium | 1.5h |\n 284→| T-907 | Low | 0.5h |\n 285→| **Total** | — | **24h** |\n 286→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4f9e54d751a312093867919dbc","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:11:46.726Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"5bb352fe-def1-4338-9625-e02370175e47","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde4fed1899dc41ba85d4793dfd25","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→/**\n   2→ * Command Registry\n   3→ * Manages command registration, lookup, and metadata.\n   4→ */\n   5→\n   6→/**\n   7→ * @typedef {Object} ParamMeta\n   8→ * @property {string} name - Parameter name\n   9→ * @property {boolean} required - Whether the parameter is required\n  10→ * @property {string} description - Parameter description\n  11→ * @property {string} [type] - Parameter type (string, number, enum)\n  12→ * @property {string[]} [enum] - Allowed values for enum type\n  13→ * @property {*} [default] - Default value\n  14→ */\n  15→\n  16→/**\n  17→ * @typedef {Object} SubcommandMeta\n  18→ * @property {string} name - Subcommand name\n  19→ * @property {string} description - Subcommand description\n  20→ * @property {ParamMeta[]} [params] - Subcommand parameters\n  21→ */\n  22→\n  23→/**\n  24→ * @typedef {Object} CommandMeta\n  25→ * @property {string} name - Command name\n  26→ * @property {string[]} [aliases] - Command aliases\n  27→ * @property {string} description - Command description\n  28→ * @property {string} usage - Usage example\n  29→ * @property {string[]} [examples] - Usage examples\n  30→ * @property {SubcommandMeta[]} [subcommands] - Available subcommands\n  31→ * @property {ParamMeta[]} [params] - Command parameters\n  32→ * @property {boolean} requiresAuth - Whether authorization is required\n  33→ * @property {string} helpText - Help text for the command\n  34→ */\n  35→\n  36→/**\n  37→ * @typedef {Object} CommandEntry\n  38→ * @property {CommandMeta} meta - Command metadata\n  39→ * @property {Function} handler - Command handler function\n  40→ */\n  41→\n  42→/**\n  43→ * @typedef {import('./parser.js').ParsedCommand} ParsedCommand\n  44→ */\n  45→\n  46→// Internal registry storage\n  47→const commands = new Map();\n  48→const aliasToCommand = new Map();\n  49→\n  50→/**\n  51→ * Register a command with its metadata and handler.\n  52→ * @param {CommandMeta} meta - Command metadata\n  53→ * @param {Function} handler - Command handler function\n  54→ * @throws {Error} If command already registered\n  55→ */\n  56→export function registerCommand(meta, handler) {\n  57→  if (!meta || !meta.name) {\n  58→    throw new Error('Command meta must have a name');\n  59→  }\n  60→\n  61→  // Normalize meta with lowercase name\n  62→  const normalizedMeta = {\n  63→    ...meta,\n  64→    name: meta.name.toLowerCase()\n  65→  };\n  66→  const name = normalizedMeta.name;\n  67→\n  68→  if (commands.has(name)) {\n  69→    throw new Error(`Command \"${name}\" is already registered`);\n  70→  }\n  71→\n  72→  // Register command\n  73→  commands.set(name, { meta: normalizedMeta, handler });\n  74→\n  75→  // Register aliases\n  76→  if (meta.aliases && Array.isArray(meta.aliases)) {\n  77→    for (const alias of meta.aliases) {\n  78→      const aliasLower = alias.toLowerCase();\n  79→      if (aliasToCommand.has(aliasLower)) {\n  80→        throw new Error(`Alias \"${alias}\" is already registered`);\n  81→      }\n  82→      aliasToCommand.set(aliasLower, name);\n  83→    }\n  84→  }\n  85→}\n  86→\n  87→/**\n  88→ * Get a command entry by name or alias.\n  89→ * @param {string} name - Command name or alias\n  90→ * @returns {CommandEntry | null} Command entry or null\n  91→ */\n  92→export function getCommand(name) {\n  93→  if (!name || typeof name !== 'string') {\n  94→    return null;\n  95→  }\n  96→\n  97→  const nameLower = name.toLowerCase();\n  98→\n  99→  // Try direct lookup\n 100→  if (commands.has(nameLower)) {\n 101→    return commands.get(nameLower);\n 102→  }\n 103→\n 104→  // Try alias lookup\n 105→  const resolvedName = aliasToCommand.get(nameLower);\n 106→  if (resolvedName && commands.has(resolvedName)) {\n 107→    return commands.get(resolvedName);\n 108→  }\n 109→\n 110→  return null;\n 111→}\n 112→\n 113→/**\n 114→ * Check if a name is a registered alias.\n 115→ * @param {string} name - Name to check\n 116→ * @returns {boolean} True if name is an alias\n 117→ */\n 118→export function isAlias(name) {\n 119→  if (!name || typeof name !== 'string') {\n 120→    return false;\n 121→  }\n 122→  return aliasToCommand.has(name.toLowerCase());\n 123→}\n 124→\n 125→/**\n 126→ * Get all registered commands.\n 127→ * @returns {CommandEntry[]} All command entries\n 128→ */\n 129→export function getAllCommands() {\n 130→  return Array.from(commands.values());\n 131→}\n 132→\n 133→/**\n 134→ * Generate help text for a specific command or all commands.\n 135→ * @param {string} [commandName] - Optional command name for specific help\n 136→ * @returns {string} Help text\n 137→ */\n 138→export function getHelpText(commandName) {\n 139→  if (commandName) {\n 140→    const entry = getCommand(commandName);\n 141→    if (!entry) {\n 142→      return `未知命令 '${commandName}'。输入 /help 查看可用命令。`;\n 143→    }\n 144→    return formatCommandHelp(entry.meta);\n 145→  }\n 146→\n 147→  // Generate general help\n 148→  const commandList = getAllCommands()\n 149→    .map((entry) => {\n 150→      const aliases = entry.meta.aliases?.length ? ` (${entry.meta.aliases.map((a) => `/${a}`).join(', ')})` : '';\n 151→      return `/${entry.meta.name}${aliases} - ${entry.meta.description}`;\n 152→    })\n 153→    .sort();\n 154→\n 155→  return `可用命令：\\n\\n${commandList.join('\\n')}`;\n 156→}\n 157→\n 158→/**\n 159→ * Format detailed help for a single command.\n 160→ * @param {CommandMeta} meta - Command metadata\n 161→ * @returns {string} Formatted help text\n 162→ */\n 163→function formatCommandHelp(meta) {\n 164→  const lines = [`/${meta.name} - ${meta.description}`];\n 165→\n 166→  if (meta.aliases?.length) {\n 167→    lines.push(`别名: ${meta.aliases.map((a) => `/${a}`).join(', ')}`);\n 168→  }\n 169→\n 170→  if (meta.usage) {\n 171→    lines.push(`用法: ${meta.usage}`);\n 172→  }\n 173→\n 174→  if (meta.subcommands?.length) {\n 175→    lines.push('\\n子命令:');\n 176→    for (const sub of meta.subcommands) {\n 177→      lines.push(`  ${sub.name} - ${sub.description}`);\n 178→    }\n 179→  }\n 180→\n 181→  if (meta.params?.length) {\n 182→    lines.push('\\n参数:');\n 183→    for (const param of meta.params) {\n 184→      const required = param.required ? '(必填)' : '(可选)';\n 185→      lines.push(`  ${param.name} ${required} - ${param.description}`);\n 186→    }\n 187→  }\n 188→\n 189→  if (meta.examples?.length) {\n 190→    lines.push('\\n示例:');\n 191→    for (const example of meta.examples) {\n 192→      lines.push(`  ${example}`);\n 193→    }\n 194→  }\n 195→\n 196→  return lines.join('\\n');\n 197→}\n 198→\n 199→/**\n 200→ * Clear the registry (for testing).\n 201→ */\n 202→export function clearRegistry() {\n 203→  commands.clear();\n 204→  aliasToCommand.clear();\n 205→}\n 206→\n 207→/**\n 208→ * Get the alias map for parser usage.\n 209→ * @returns {Record<string, string>} Alias to command name mapping\n 210→ */\n 211→export function getAliasMap() {\n 212→  const map = {};\n 213→  for (const [alias, command] of aliasToCommand) {\n 214→    map[alias] = command;\n 215→  }\n 216→  return map;\n 217→}\n 218→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4f9e54d751a312093867919dbc","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:11:46.730Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
