{"type":"user","uuid":"3e56671d-25d2-4541-873f-1d18e9dbd0ed","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde531c33b8b98bb9265ba6782aec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Command: cd /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw && git diff --stat 2>&1\nStdout:  .prizm-docs/changelog.prizm          |  1 +\n .prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm        |  2 +\n feature-list.json                    |  2 +-\n src/bot/commands/validator.js        | 43 ++++++++++++-------\n tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js | 80 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n 5 files changed, 113 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)\n\nStderr: (empty)\nExit Code: 0\nSignal: (none)"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4f9e54d751a312093867919dbc","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:15.332Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"fd2910c4-ad07-40e8-a34c-d2cc35718b30","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde4f9e54d751a312093867919dbc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary: F002-CRIT-001 Bug Fix Complete\n\n### Issue\nThe parser always treated the first non-option token as a subcommand, regardless of whether the command has subcommands defined. This caused positional arguments like `/bugfix session-123` to be incorrectly parsed as `subcommand: \"session-123\"` instead of being recognized as the `target` parameter.\n\n### Fix Applied\nModified `src/bot/commands/validator.js` to:\n1. Check if the command has no subcommands defined\n2. When no subcommands exist, use `parsed.subcommand` as the first positional parameter source\n3. Map positional arguments by parameter index for proper parameter binding\n\n### Changes Made\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/bot/commands/validator.js` | Modified `getParamValue()` to accept metadata and parameter index, fallback to `parsed.subcommand` as first positional when command has no subcommands |\n| `tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js` | Added 5 new tests for bugfix, logs, stop commands and edge cases |\n| `.prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm` | Added TRAP entry for F002-CRIT-001 and DECISION documenting fix |\n| `.prizm-docs/changelog.prizm` | Added changelog entry for the bug fix |\n\n### Test Results\n- **Validator tests**: 19 pass, 0 fail\n- **All command tests**: 75 pass, 0 fail\n- **Integration tests**: 46 pass, 0 fail\n- **Typecheck**: Clean\n- **Lint**: Clean\n\n### Acceptance Criteria Met\n- ✅ `/bugfix session-123` correctly passes `target: \"session-123\"` to handler\n- ✅ `/logs my-feature` correctly passes `target: \"my-feature\"` to handler\n- ✅ `/stop my-feature` correctly passes `target: \"my-feature\"` to handler\n- ✅ All existing tests still pass\n- ✅ New tests added to prevent regression\n\n[Agent ID: agent-722d8569]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4f9e54d751a312093867919dbc","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:23.464Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
