{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312031531350531b4c870457c","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"id":"20260312031531350531b4c870457c","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_4df7d102c78646598db0be4f","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/002-telegram-pipeline-command-router/tasks.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":10901,"output_tokens":338,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde534b4a280ed48c1d7bb99ac931","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:40.397Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"4adb3927-eb32-4c90-90fb-54e9fa25ce19","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_1aef4d50c583462cb18ee87e","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-reviewer\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated quality reviewer. Uses prizmkit.analyze for cross-document consistency, prizmkit.code-review for spec compliance and code quality, and writes integration tests. Use when performing analysis, testing, or code review.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-code-review, prizmkit-analyze, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **Reviewer Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的质量审查员。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"质检员 + 校对员\"——不生产产品但确保质量，负责两个阶段的工作：\n  14→1. **交叉校验（Phase 4）**: 在实现前用 `prizmkit.analyze` 检查 spec/plan/tasks 的一致性\n  15→2. **评审（Phase 6）**: 在实现后用 `prizmkit.code-review` 检查代码质量，编写和执行集成测试\n  16→\n  17→### 项目上下文\n  18→\n  19→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。审查前先读 `root.prizm` 了解项目规则（RULES）、模式（PATTERNS）和已知陷阱（TRAPS），需要时读取模块级文档。\n  20→\n  21→### 制品路径\n  22→\n  23→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  24→|------|------|\n  25→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 规则、模式、已知陷阱 |\n  26→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  27→\n  28→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  29→\n  30→1. Phase 4 时运行 `prizmkit.analyze` 做交叉一致性校验\n  31→2. Phase 6 时运行 `prizmkit.code-review` 做规格合规和代码质量审查\n  32→3. Phase 6 时编写和执行集成测试，验证模块间交互\n  33→4. 验证实际实现是否符合 plan.md 中的接口设计\n  34→5. 验证跨模块数据流的完整性和正确性\n  35→6. 测试边界条件和异常路径\n  36→7. 检查代码是否符合 `.prizm-docs/` RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  37→8. 审查是**只读操作**（Phase 4 和 Phase 6 的审查部分不修改代码文件）\n  38→9. 集成测试用例必须覆盖 spec.md 定义的所有用户故事\n  39→\n  40→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  41→\n  42→- 不编写实现代码（Dev 的职责）\n  43→- 不分解任务（PM 的职责）\n  44→- 不进行任务调度（Coordinator 的职责）\n  45→\n  46→### 行为规则\n  47→\n  48→```\n  49→REV-01: Phase 4 使用 prizmkit.analyze 做交叉校验\n  50→REV-02: Phase 6 使用 prizmkit.code-review 做代码审查\n  51→REV-03: 每个发现必须引用具体的文件路径和行号\n  52→REV-04: CRITICAL 级别发现必须包含具体的修复建议\n  53→REV-05: 最多 30 个发现（保持可操作性）\n  54→REV-06: Spec compliance 失败始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  55→REV-07: 安全发现始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  56→REV-08: 集成测试必须覆盖 spec.md 所有用户故事\n  57→REV-09: 审查代码是否符合 .prizm-docs/ PATTERNS 和 RULES\n  58→```\n  59→\n  60→### Phase 4 工作流程：交叉校验\n  61→\n  62→**前置条件**: PM 已完成 spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md\n  63→\n  64→1. 运行 `prizmkit.analyze`（只读）\n  65→   - 输入: spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md\n  66→   - 6 个检测通道: 重复检测、歧义检测、不完整检测、Prizm 规则对齐、覆盖缺口、不一致性\n  67→   - 输出: 一致性分析报告（仅对话输出）\n  68→2. 如发现 CRITICAL 问题，报告给 Coordinator 退回 PM 修复\n  69→3. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含分析结果）\n  70→\n  71→### Phase 6 工作流程：评审\n  72→\n  73→**前置条件**: Dev 已完成实现，所有任务标记 `[x]`\n  74→\n  75→1. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm`，重点关注 RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  76→2. 运行 `prizmkit.code-review`（只读）\n  77→   - 6 个审查维度: 规格符合度、计划遵循度、代码质量、安全性、一致性、测试覆盖\n  78→   - 判定: PASS | PASS WITH WARNINGS | NEEDS FIXES\n  79→3. 编写和执行集成测试:\n  80→   - 接口合规性（请求格式、响应格式）\n  81→   - 跨模块数据流完整性\n  82→   - 用户故事验收标准（来自 spec.md）\n  83→   - 边界条件和异常路径\n  84→4. 生成统一评审报告\n  85→5. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）\n  86→\n  87→### 判定标准\n  88→\n  89→| 判定 | 条件 | 后续动作 |\n  90→|------|------|---------|\n  91→| **PASS** | 无 CRITICAL 或 HIGH 发现 | 进入下一阶段 |\n  92→| **PASS_WITH_WARNINGS** | 无 CRITICAL，有 HIGH 发现 | 记录待改进项，可进入下一阶段 |\n  93→| **NEEDS_FIXES** | 存在 CRITICAL 发现 | 退回 Dev 修复后重新评审 |\n  94→\n  95→### 严重级别\n  96→\n  97→| 级别 | 定义 | 示例 |\n  98→|------|------|------|\n  99→| CRITICAL | 安全风险或严重架构问题 | SQL 注入、硬编码密钥 |\n 100→| HIGH | 影响可维护性的显著问题 | 规格不符、大量重复代码 |\n 101→| MEDIUM | 代码质量改进点 | 命名不统一、缺少注释 |\n 102→| LOW | 风格建议 | 格式微调、可选优化 |\n 103→\n 104→### 异常处理\n 105→\n 106→| 场景 | 策略 |\n 107→|------|------|\n 108→| analyze 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 PM 修复 |\n 109→| code-review 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 Dev 修复 |\n 110→| 集成测试失败 | 分类严重级别 → ISSUE_REPORT → Coordinator 派发给 Dev |\n 111→| 审查发现超过 30 个 | 只保留最严重的 30 个 |\n 112→| Prizm RULES 违规 | 自动标记为 CRITICAL |\n 113→\n 114→### 通信规则\n 115→\n 116→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n 117→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）标志完成\n 118→- 发送 ISSUE_REPORT 报告 CRITICAL 发现\n 119→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 120→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde534b4a280ed48c1d7bb99ac931","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:40.398Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"3ad3191e-5897-48f3-a155-8ec431d5adeb","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_100809960d5d48118190f295","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L0\n   2→PROJECT_NAME: PrizmClaw\n   3→PROJECT_TYPE: telegram-bridge + web-api\n   4→ADOPTION_MODE: brownfield\n   5→PLATFORM: codebuddy\n   6→LANGUAGES: JavaScript(ESM), HTML, CSS, Python, Shell\n   7→PACKAGE_MANAGER: npm\n   8→ENTRYPOINTS: src/index.js -> src/http/server.js + src/bot/telegram.js\n   9→DOC_STATUS: initialized\n  10→ASSESSMENT: ASSESSMENT.md\n  11→MIGRATION_CANDIDATE: docs/AI_CONTEXT -> not_found\n  12→\n  13→MODULE_INDEX:\n  14→- runtime: src/** -> .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n  15→- web-ui: public/** -> .prizm-docs/web-ui.prizm\n  16→- pipeline: dev-pipeline/** -> .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n  17→- dev-team: dev-team/** -> .prizm-docs/team.prizm\n  18→- project-config: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md -> .prizm-docs/config.prizm\n  19→\n  20→LOAD_RULES:\n  21→- ON_SESSION_START: read .prizm-docs/root.prizm\n  22→- ON_TASK: load related L1 via MODULE_INDEX\n  23→- ON_EDIT: load/create related L2 lazily\n  24→\n  25→DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:\n  26→- outdated_major: dotenv,express,zod\n  27→- npm_audit_prod: 0 vulnerabilities\n  28→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde534b4a280ed48c1d7bb99ac931","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:40.399Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"13919cb1-7009-4a1e-bb1d-dacab5d9a591","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_17795e17e9e24a9dbecb9771","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-002: Telegram Pipeline Command Router\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→在 Telegram Bot 中新增管道控制命令路由层，支持解析与分发 `/pipeline`、`/bugfix`、`/planner`、`/status`、`/logs`、`/stop` 等命令，将参数规范化后交给后端控制模块执行。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 命令语义解析、参数验证、权限检查、路由分发。不包含长任务执行。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-001 (Project Infrastructure Setup) — completed\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: Pipeline Command\n  16→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/pipeline [action] [target]` 命令启动或查询 feature 管道。\n  17→\n  18→**Note**: `/planner` 命令作为 `/pipeline` 的管道类型变体（type=planner），行为相同，故包含在本 US 范围内（见 D1）。\n  19→\n  20→**Example**:\n  21→- `/pipeline run my-feature` — 启动管道\n  22→- `/pipeline status` — 查询状态\n  23→- `/pipeline logs my-feature` — 查看日志\n  24→- `/planner run my-feature` — 启动 planner 类型管道\n  25→\n  26→**Acceptance**:\n  27→- 支持 `run`, `status`, `logs`, `stop` 子命令\n  28→- `target` 参数可选，默认当前工作目录\n  29→- 无效子命令返回帮助提示\n  30→- `/planner` 行为等同于 `/pipeline --type=planner`\n  31→\n  32→---\n  33→\n  34→### US-2: Bugfix Command\n  35→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/bugfix [target]` 快捷命令启动 bugfix 管道。\n  36→\n  37→**Example**:\n  38→- `/bugfix session-123` — 启动 bugfix 管道\n  39→\n  40→**Acceptance**:\n  41→- 等同于 `/pipeline run --type=bugfix <target>`\n  42→- 参数缺失时返回使用说明\n  43→\n  44→---\n  45→\n  46→### US-3: Status Query\n  47→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/status` 查看当前管道状态。\n  48→\n  49→**Example**:\n  50→- `/status` — 显示所有运行中的管道\n  51→\n  52→**Acceptance**:\n  53→- 返回管道列表 + 状态摘要\n  54→- 无运行管道时返回提示\n  55→\n  56→---\n  57→\n  58→### US-4: Logs Query\n  59→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/logs [target]` 查看管道日志。\n  60→\n  61→**Example**:\n  62→- `/logs` — 最近管道日志\n  63→- `/logs session-123` — 指定目标日志\n  64→\n  65→**Acceptance**:\n  66→- 支持分页或截断显示\n  67→- 日志过长时发送为文件\n  68→\n  69→---\n  70→\n  71→### US-5: Stop Pipeline\n  72→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/stop [target]` 停止运行中的管道。\n  73→\n  74→**Example**:\n  75→- `/stop` — 停止当前管道\n  76→- `/stop session-123` — 停止指定管道\n  77→\n  78→**Acceptance**:\n  79→- 确认停止操作\n  80→- 返回停止结果\n  81→\n  82→---\n  83→\n  84→### US-6: Error Guidance\n  85→作为用户，当我输入错误参数时，系统返回明确的修正建议。\n  86→\n  87→**Example**:\n  88→- `/pipeline xyz` → \"未知子命令 'xyz'。可用: run, status, logs, stop\"\n  89→\n  90→**Acceptance**:\n  91→- 参数错误有明确提示\n  92→- 提供正确的命令示例\n  93→\n  94→---\n  95→\n  96→### US-7: Authorization Guard\n  97→作为未授权用户，我无法调用管道命令，且收到统一拒绝提示。\n  98→\n  99→**Acceptance**:\n 100→- 所有管道命令需授权检查\n 101→- 统一拒绝消息（不暴露敏感信息）\n 102→\n 103→---\n 104→\n 105→## Non-Functional Requirements\n 106→\n 107→### NFR-1: Extensibility\n 108→- 命令路由层支持注册新命令\n 109→- 参数解析器可扩展\n 110→\n 111→### NFR-2: Testability\n 112→- Handler 接口可 mock\n 113→- 权限检查可 mock\n 114→\n 115→### NFR-3: Performance\n 116→- 命令解析 < 50ms\n 117→- 不阻塞 Telegram webhook\n 118→\n 119→---\n 120→\n 121→## Scope Boundaries\n 122→\n 123→### In Scope\n 124→- 命令解析与路由\n 125→- 参数规范化\n 126→- 权限检查\n 127→- 帮助文本生成\n 128→- 错误提示\n 129→\n 130→### Out of Scope\n 131→- 长任务执行（由 pipeline-control-service 处理）\n 132→- Pipeline 内部逻辑\n 133→- 持久化存储\n 134→- Web UI\n 135→\n 136→---\n 137→\n 138→## Command Reference\n 139→\n 140→| Command | Subcommands | Params | Handler |\n 141→|---------|-------------|--------|---------|\n 142→| `/pipeline` | run, status, logs, stop | `[target]`, `[--type=]` | pipelineHandler |\n 143→| `/bugfix` | — | `<target>` | bugfixHandler |\n 144→| `/planner` | run, status, logs | `[target]` | plannerHandler |\n 145→| `/status` | — | — | statusHandler |\n 146→| `/logs` | — | `[target]` | logsHandler |\n 147→| `/stop` | — | `[target]` | stopHandler |\n 148→\n 149→---\n 150→\n 151→## Alias Mapping\n 152→\n 153→| Alias | Maps To |\n 154→|-------|---------|\n 155→| `/p` | `/pipeline` |\n 156→| `/b` | `/bugfix` |\n 157→| `/s` | `/status` |\n 158→| `/l` | `/logs` |\n 159→\n 160→---\n 161→\n 162→## Decisions\n 163→\n 164→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 165→|----|------|----------|\n 166→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | `/planner` 为独立管道类型，行为同 `/pipeline`，默认 `type=planner` |\n 167→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 复用现有 `isAllowedUser()` 进行授权检查，分级权限留作后续扩展 |\n 168→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 日志 < 4000 字符分块发送，>= 4000 字符发送为文件 |\n 169→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde534b4a280ed48c1d7bb99ac931","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:40.399Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"b5da6e3d-f028-4c35-9d30-b6a1a4eda32f","session_id":"c7a56f37-52f8-4378-9a28-e0cf90afeea0","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_cfcc5f53d11d4c0a8e519685","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-002: Technical Implementation Plan\n   2→\n   3→## Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                     Telegram Bot Entry                       │\n   8→│                   src/bot/telegram.js                        │\n   9→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  10→                              │\n  11→                              ▼\n  12→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  13→│                   Command Router Layer                       │\n  14→│              src/bot/commands/index.js                       │\n  15→│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n  16→│  │   Parser     │  │   Registry   │  │  Validator   │      │\n  17→│  │ parseCommand │  │ commandMap   │  │ validateArgs │      │\n  18→│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n  19→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  20→                              │\n  21→                              ▼\n  22→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  23→│                    Command Handlers                          │\n  24→│                 src/bot/commands/handlers/                   │\n  25→│  ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌──────────┐ │\n  26→│  │ pipeline   │ │ bugfix     │ │ status     │ │ logs     │ │\n  27→│  │ Handler    │ │ Handler    │ │ Handler    │ │ Handler  │ │\n  28→│  └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └──────────┘ │\n  29→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  30→                              │\n  31→                              ▼\n  32→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  33→│              Pipeline Control Service (F-001)                │\n  34→│          src/services/pipeline-control-service.js            │\n  35→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  36→```\n  37→\n  38→---\n  39→\n  40→## Component Design\n  41→\n  42→### 1. Command Parser (`src/bot/commands/parser.js`)\n  43→\n  44→**Purpose**: 解析 Telegram 消息文本为结构化命令对象。\n  45→\n  46→**Interface**:\n  47→```typescript\n  48→interface ParsedCommand {\n  49→  command: string;      // e.g., \"pipeline\"\n  50→  subcommand?: string;  // e.g., \"run\"\n  51→  args: string[];       // positional args\n  52→  options: Record<string, string>; // --key=value\n  53→  raw: string;          // original text\n  54→}\n  55→\n  56→function parseCommand(text: string): ParsedCommand | null;\n  57→```\n  58→\n  59→**Logic**:\n  60→1. 提取命令名（第一个 token，去掉 `/`）\n  61→2. 解析别名映射\n  62→3. 提取子命令（如果有）\n  63→4. 解析 `--key=value` 选项\n  64→5. 收集位置参数\n  65→\n  66→---\n  67→\n  68→### 2. Command Registry (`src/bot/commands/registry.js`)\n  69→\n  70→**Purpose**: 注册命令及其元数据，支持动态扩展。\n  71→\n  72→**Interface**:\n  73→```typescript\n  74→interface CommandMeta {\n  75→  name: string;\n  76→  aliases: string[];\n  77→  subcommands?: string[];\n  78→  params: ParamMeta[];\n  79→  requiresAuth: boolean;\n  80→  helpText: string;\n  81→}\n  82→\n  83→interface ParamMeta {\n  84→  name: string;\n  85→  required: boolean;\n  86→  description: string;\n  87→}\n  88→\n  89→function registerCommand(meta: CommandMeta, handler: CommandHandler): void;\n  90→function getCommand(name: string): CommandEntry | null;\n  91→function getHelpText(command?: string): string;\n  92→```\n  93→\n  94→---\n  95→\n  96→### 3. Command Validator (`src/bot/commands/validator.js`)\n  97→\n  98→**Purpose**: 验证命令参数，生成错误提示。\n  99→\n 100→**Interface**:\n 101→```typescript\n 102→interface ValidationResult {\n 103→  valid: boolean;\n 104→  errors: ValidationError[];\n 105→  normalized?: NormalizedParams;\n 106→}\n 107→\n 108→interface ValidationError {\n 109→  param: string;\n 110→  message: string;\n 111→  suggestion?: string;\n 112→}\n 113→\n 114→function validateCommand(parsed: ParsedCommand, meta: CommandMeta): ValidationResult;\n 115→```\n 116→\n 117→---\n 118→\n 119→### 4. Command Handlers\n 120→\n 121→#### Pipeline Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js`)\n 122→\n 123→```typescript\n 124→interface PipelineParams {\n 125→  action: 'run' | 'status' | 'logs' | 'stop';\n 126→  target?: string;\n 127→  type?: 'feature' | 'bugfix' | 'planner';\n 128→}\n 129→\n 130→async function handlePipeline(ctx: Context, params: PipelineParams): Promise<void>;\n 131→```\n 132→\n 133→**Mapping to pipeline-control-service**:\n 134→- `run` → `startPipeline({ pipelineType, targetId })`\n 135→- `status` → `getPipelineStatus({})`\n 136→- `logs` → `getPipelineLogs({ targetId })`\n 137→- `stop` → `stopPipeline({ targetId })`\n 138→\n 139→#### Bugfix Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/bugfix.js`)\n 140→\n 141→```typescript\n 142→async function handleBugfix(ctx: Context, target: string): Promise<void> {\n 143→  // Delegates to handlePipeline with type=bugfix\n 144→  return handlePipeline(ctx, { action: 'run', target, type: 'bugfix' });\n 145→}\n 146→```\n 147→\n 148→#### Status Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`)\n 149→\n 150→```typescript\n 151→async function handleStatus(ctx: Context): Promise<void> {\n 152→  // Calls getPipelineStatus({}) and formats output\n 153→}\n 154→```\n 155→\n 156→#### Logs Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`)\n 157→\n 158→```typescript\n 159→async function handleLogs(ctx: Context, target?: string): Promise<void> {\n 160→  // Calls getPipelineLogs({ targetId })\n 161→  // If output >= 4000 chars, send as file\n 162→}\n 163→```\n 164→\n 165→#### Stop Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js`)\n 166→\n 167→```typescript\n 168→async function handleStop(ctx: Context, target?: string): Promise<void> {\n 169→  // Calls stopPipeline({ targetId })\n 170→  // Shows confirmation\n 171→}\n 172→```\n 173→\n 174→---\n 175→\n 176→## Data Models\n 177→\n 178→### CommandDefinition\n 179→```typescript\n 180→interface CommandDefinition {\n 181→  name: string;\n 182→  aliases: string[];\n 183→  description: string;\n 184→  usage: string;\n 185→  examples: string[];\n 186→  subcommands?: SubcommandDefinition[];\n 187→  params?: ParamDefinition[];\n 188→  requiresAuth: boolean;\n 189→}\n 190→```\n 191→\n 192→### SubcommandDefinition\n 193→```typescript\n 194→interface SubcommandDefinition {\n 195→  name: string;\n 196→  description: string;\n 197→  params?: ParamDefinition[];\n 198→}\n 199→```\n 200→\n 201→### ParamDefinition\n 202→```typescript\n 203→interface ParamDefinition {\n 204→  name: string;\n 205→  type: 'string' | 'number' | 'enum';\n 206→  required: boolean;\n 207→  default?: any;\n 208→  enum?: string[];\n 209→  description: string;\n 210→}\n 211→```\n 212→\n 213→---\n 214→\n 215→## Command Definitions\n 216→\n 217→### /pipeline\n 218→```yaml\n 219→name: pipeline\n 220→aliases: [p]\n 221→subcommands:\n 222→  - name: run\n 223→    params:\n 224→      - name: target\n 225→        type: string\n 226→        required: false\n 227→        description: 目标标识符\n 228→      - name: type\n 229→        type: enum\n 230→        enum: [feature, bugfix, planner]\n 231→        default: feature\n 232→  - name: status\n 233→  - name: logs\n 234→    params:\n 235→      - name: target\n 236→        type: string\n 237→        required: false\n 238→  - name: stop\n 239→    params:\n 240→      - name: target\n 241→        type: string\n 242→        required: false\n 243→```\n 244→\n 245→### /bugfix\n 246→```yaml\n 247→name: bugfix\n 248→aliases: [b]\n 249→params:\n 250→  - name: target\n 251→    type: string\n 252→    required: true\n 253→# Equivalent to: /pipeline run --type=bugfix <target>\n 254→```\n 255→\n 256→### /planner\n 257→```yaml\n 258→name: planner\n 259→aliases: []\n 260→subcommands:\n 261→  - name: run\n 262→    params:\n 263→      - name: target\n 264→        type: string\n 265→        required: false\n 266→  - name: status\n 267→  - name: logs\n 268→# Equivalent to: /pipeline run --type=planner <target>\n 269→```\n 270→\n 271→### /status\n 272→```yaml\n 273→name: status\n 274→aliases: [s]\n 275→# Shows all running pipelines\n 276→```\n 277→\n 278→### /logs\n 279→```yaml\n 280→name: logs\n 281→aliases: [l]\n 282→params:\n 283→  - name: target\n 284→    type: string\n 285→    required: false\n 286→```\n 287→\n 288→### /stop\n 289→```yaml\n 290→name: stop\n 291→params:\n 292→  - name: target\n 293→    type: string\n 294→    required: false\n 295→```\n 296→\n 297→---\n 298→\n 299→## Module Dependencies\n 300→\n 301→```\n 302→src/bot/commands/\n 303→├── index.js          # Router entry point\n 304→├── parser.js         # Command parsing\n 305→├── registry.js       # Command registration\n 306→├── validator.js      # Parameter validation\n 307→├── formatter.js      # Output formatting\n 308→├── help.js           # Help text generation\n 309→└── handlers/\n 310→    ├── pipeline.js\n 311→    ├── bugfix.js\n 312→    ├── planner.js\n 313→    ├── status.js\n 314→    ├── logs.js\n 315→    └── stop.js\n 316→\n 317→Dependencies:\n 318→├── src/services/pipeline-control-service.js (F-001)\n 319→├── src/security/guard.js (existing)\n 320→└── src/utils/logger.js (existing)\n 321→```\n 322→\n 323→---\n 324→\n 325→## API Specification\n 326→\n 327→### Router API (`src/bot/commands/index.js`)\n 328→\n 329→```typescript\n 330→// Main router function\n 331→export async function routeCommand(ctx: Context): Promise<boolean>;\n 332→\n 333→// Returns true if command was handled, false otherwise\n 334→// Handles auth check, parsing, validation, and dispatch\n 335→```\n 336→\n 337→### Handler Interface\n 338→\n 339→```typescript\n 340→interface CommandHandler {\n 341→  (ctx: Context, params: Record<string, any>): Promise<void>;\n 342→}\n 343→\n 344→interface HandlerContext {\n 345→  ctx: Context;           // Telegram context\n 346→  parsed: ParsedCommand;  // Parsed command\n 347→  meta: CommandMeta;      // Command metadata\n 348→  reply: (text: string) => Promise<void>;\n 349→  replyFile: (content: string, filename: string) => Promise<void>;\n 350→}\n 351→```\n 352→\n 353→---\n 354→\n 355→## Error Handling\n 356→\n 357→### Error Types\n 358→\n 359→| Code | Message | Example |\n 360→|------|---------|---------|\n 361→| `UNKNOWN_COMMAND` | 未知命令 '{cmd}'。输入 /help 查看可用命令。 | `/xyz` |\n 362→| `UNKNOWN_SUBCOMMAND` | 未知子命令 '{sub}'。可用: {list} | `/pipeline xyz` |\n 363→| `MISSING_PARAM` | 缺少参数 '{param}'。用法: {usage} | `/bugfix` |\n 364→| `INVALID_PARAM` | 参数 '{param}' 无效: {reason} | `/pipeline run --type=xyz` |\n 365→| `UNAUTHORIZED` | 当前账号未被授权使用该命令。 | 未授权用户 |\n 366→\n 367→### Error Response Format\n 368→\n 369→```typescript\n 370→interface ErrorResponse {\n 371→  code: string;\n 372→  message: string;\n 373→  suggestion?: string;\n 374→  usage?: string;\n 375→}\n 376→\n 377→function formatError(error: ErrorResponse): string;\n 378→```\n 379→\n 380→---\n 381→\n 382→## Test Strategy\n 383→\n 384→### Unit Tests\n 385→\n 386→| Module | Test Cases |\n 387→|--------|------------|\n 388→| `parser.js` | 解析各种命令格式、别名、选项 |\n 389→| `registry.js` | 注册、查找、别名映射 |\n 390→| `validator.js` | 必填参数、类型检查、枚举值 |\n 391→| `handlers/*.js` | Mock pipeline-control-service，验证调用参数 |\n 392→\n 393→### Integration Tests\n 394→\n 395→| Scenario | Test |\n 396→|----------|------|\n 397→| E2E command flow | 模拟 Telegram 消息，验证完整流程 |\n 398→| Auth guard | 验证未授权用户被拦截 |\n 399→| Error messages | 验证错误消息格式 |\n 400→\n 401→### Test Files\n 402→\n 403→```\n 404→tests/bot/commands/\n 405→├── parser.test.js\n 406→├── registry.test.js\n 407→├── validator.test.js\n 408→├── handlers/\n 409→│   ├── pipeline.test.js\n 410→│   ├── bugfix.test.js\n 411→│   └── status.test.js\n 412→└── integration/\n 413→    └── command-router.test.js\n 414→```\n 415→\n 416→---\n 417→\n 418→## Risk Assessment\n 419→\n 420→| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\n 421→|------|------------|--------|------------|\n 422→| 命令解析错误 | Medium | Medium | 完善测试覆盖，提供清晰错误提示 |\n 423→| 权限绕过 | Low | High | 统一权限检查层，避免遗漏 |\n 424→| 性能阻塞 | Low | Medium | 确保解析轻量，长操作异步 |\n 425→| 命令冲突 | Low | Low | Registry 检查重复注册 |\n 426→\n 427→---\n 428→\n 429→## User Story Mapping\n 430→\n 431→| User Story | Components | Tasks |\n 432→|------------|------------|-------|\n 433→| US-1: Pipeline | parser, registry, pipeline-handler, planner-handler | T-100, T-106 |\n 434→| US-2: Bugfix | parser, registry, bugfix-handler | T-101 |\n 435→| US-3: Status | parser, registry, status-handler | T-102 |\n 436→| US-4: Logs | parser, registry, logs-handler | T-103 |\n 437→| US-5: Stop | parser, registry, stop-handler | T-104 |\n 438→| US-6: Error Guidance | validator, formatter | T-013, T-105 |\n 439→| US-7: Authorization | registry (requiresAuth) | T-010 |\n 440→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde534b4a280ed48c1d7bb99ac931","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:15:40.400Z","_requestId":"33c1fe9f6f094d499ac61721329a98f3"}
